8.15 Likewise, we recommended and the Management agreed to:
a. Require the BAC to strictly comply with all the procedures prescribed by RA No. 9184 and its revised IRR;
b. Instruct the Municipal Accountant to ensure that all documents as required by RA No. 9184 and COA Circular No. 2012-001 be attached to the disbursement before processing of claims;
